- **Templates:** the three prompts per chunk (facts JSON, summary+lessons, advice) mirror your intended use. Add more templates if you want diversity.
- **Labels:** the scripts leave assistant outputs empty so you can (a) human‚Äëlabel a seed set, (b) generate weak labels with your current model, then (c) refine with a review pass.

