You only got one record because the script splits on **blank lines** (`\n\n+`). Your `age6.txt` has **no blank lines**‚Äîeach memory is on its own single line‚Äîso the whole file was treated as one paragraph.

Here‚Äôs a drop‚Äëin fix: a smarter splitter that works in three modes:

- **auto (default):** if the file has blank lines, use them; otherwise split on single newlines  
- **line:** always split on every non‚Äëempty line  
- **sentence:** (optional) split into sentences with a simple regex

